el|date=2020-03-19|publisher=Bloomsbury Publishing|year=|isbn=978-1-4729-8269-8|location=|pages=140|language=en}}</ref>\n\n== List of works<ref name=\":1\" />==\n\n* 1926 - Dahl (M.) (Maria), ''Spinentiere\u00a0 oder Arachnoidea. I.Spring-spinnen (Salticidae)''. Tierw. Deuts., 1926, pp.1-55, 159 fig.\n* 1927 - Dahl (M.), vide DAHL (F.) & Maria DAHL, 1927.\n* 1928 - Dahl (M.), ''Einige Lebendbeobachtungen an Argiope lobata (Arachneae, Argiopidae)''. Zool. Anz., 75 (3-4), pp.79-85\n* 1928 - Dahl (M.), ''Spinnen (Araneae) von Nowaja-Semlja''. Norsk. Vid. Akard. Oslo, 1928, pp.1-37.<ref name=\":5\">{{Cite book|last=America|first=Arctic Institute of North|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=05oZAAAAMAAJ&|title=Arctic Bibliography|date=1953|publisher=Department of Defense|year=|isbn=|location=|pages=550|language=en}}</ref>\n*1931 - Dahl (M.), ''Spinnentiere oder Arachnoidea. VI. 24 Familie: Agelenidae''. Tierw. Deuts., 1931, pp.1-46, 76 fig.\n*1933 - Dahl (M.), ''Spinnen (Araneae). in The Norwegian North Polar Expedition with the Maud 1918-1925'', Scientific Results, 5 (16), pp.3-4.<ref name=\":5\" />\n*1935 - Dahl (M.), ''Zur Kenntnis der Spinnentiere Schlesiens. A. Araneae und Opiliones''. Sitz-ber. Ges naturf. Freu. Berlin, 1935, pp.337-353.\n*1937 - Dahl (M.), ''Spinnentiere oder Arachnoidea. VIII. 19 Familie: Hahniidae''. Tierw. Deuts., 1937, pp.100-114, 33 fig.\n*1937 - Dahl (M.), ''Spinnentiere oder Arachnoidea. VIII. 20 Familie: Argyronetidae''. Tierw. Deuts., 1937, pp.115-118, fig.34-38.\n*1938 - Dahl (M.), ''Zur Verbreitung der Gattung Porrhomma in deutschen H\u00f6hlen, Stollen, Bergwerten und Kellern und deren freilebenden Arten''. Mitt. H\u00f6hl. u. Karstjorsch., 1938, pp.122 132, 9 fig.\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:German women scientists]]\n[[Category:German arachnologists]]\n\n[[Category:19th-century women scientists]]\n\n[[Category:19th-century German zoologists]]\n[[Category:German women scientists]]\n[[Category:German arachnologists]]\n[[Category:German carcinologists]]\n[[Category:19th-century women scientists]]\n[[Category:People of Ukrainian descent]]\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dahl, Maria}}\n[[Category:1872 births]]\n[[Category:1972 deaths]]\n", "name_user": "SpicyMilkBoy", "label": "safe", "comment": "ce", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maria_Dahl"}
